    "name": "Eric Sanderson",
    "profile": "Eric Sanderson is a Producer, Mixing Engineer and Multi-instrumentalist based in Brooklyn, New York with over 340,000,000 streams associated to his name. \r\n\r\nOriginally know for his work with the band Augustines, Eric now works primarily with other artist in whatever fashion they require.  He is the owner and operator of a 2000 sq ft recording studio in Red Hook, Brooklyn called Harbor Studios.  He has worked with bands such as Nicotine Dolls, Death Cab For Cutie, Augustines, Wild Rivers, Brian Fallon, The Moth and The Flame, Lullanas, The Philistines Jr, Stars, Darlingside, Allman Brown, Nick and June, and many more.  \r\n\r\nEric is currently a member of Augustines and The Philistines Jr. though neither band is actively touring. ",
